Package: TidyBlock
Title: Spreadsheet-Based GUI for Tidyverse Data Wrangling and ggplot2 Visualization
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Masakazu", "Kagawa", 
           email = "your-email@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: An open-source R Shiny application that provides a modern,
    spreadsheet-like graphical user interface over the core tidyverse and
    ggplot2 functionality. Users can import, clean, reshape, aggregate,
    join, and visualize datasets through point-and-click interactions
    without writing any R code.
